        <abstract>
            <p>Will try to get more information about the supposed hybrid [of cow and deer].</p>
            <p>The rumours about John Robinson [curate of Down] cause JBI concern. He will seek to get the facts – will try to protect Robinson against malicious rumours, but if he is immoral he must go forthwith.</p>
